<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>David Brilly | Portfolio</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        html {
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
            background-color: #0f0f0f;
            color: #eee;
        }

        /* NAV */
        nav {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            width: 100%;
            background: rgba(15,15,15,0.95);
            padding: 18px 40px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            z-index: 100;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #222;
        }

        nav .logo {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #e94560;
        }

        nav ul {
            list-style: none;
            display: flex;
            gap: 30px;
        }

        nav ul a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #aaa;
            font-size: 15px;
            transition: color 0.3s;
        }

        nav ul a:hover {
            color: #e94560;
        }

        /* HERO */
        .hero {
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f0f0f 0%, #1a1a2e 100%);
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 56px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            color: #fff;
        }

        .hero h1 span {
            color: #e94560;
        }

        .hero p {
            font-size: 20px;
            color: #aaa;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            max-width: 500px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .btn {
            padding: 14px 36px;
            background: #e94560;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 30px;
            font-size: 16px;
            cursor: pointer;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: background 0.3s, transform 0.2s;
        }

        .btn:hover {
            background: #c73652;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        /* SEKCIJE */
        section {
            padding: 90px 40px;
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        section h2 {
            font-size: 36px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            color: #fff;
            position: relative;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        section h2::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -8px;
            left: 0;
            width: 50px;
            height: 3px;
            background: #e94560;
            border-radius: 2px;
        }

        /* ABOUT */
        .about-text {
            font-size: 17px;
            line-height: 1.9;
            color: #bbb;
            max-width: 680px;
        }

        /* SKILLS */
        .skills-grid {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 12px;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        .skill-tag {
            padding: 10px 22px;
            border-radius: 30px;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 500;
            border: 1px solid #333;
            color: #ddd;
            background: #1a1a1a;
        }

        .skill-tag.highlight {
            background: #e94560;
            border-color: #e94560;
            color: white;
        }

        /* PROJECTS */
        .projects-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
            gap: 24px;
        }

        .project-card {
            background: #1a1a1a;
            border: 1px solid #2a2a2a;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 28px;
            transition: transform 0.3s, border-color 0.3s;
        }

        .project-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-6px);
            border-color: #e94560;
        }

        .project-card h3 {
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            color: #fff;
        }

        .project-card p {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #888;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }

        .project-tag {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 16px;
            padding: 4px 12px;
            background: #e9456022;
            color: #e94560;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
        }

        /* CONTACT */
        .contact-box {
            background: #1a1a1a;
            border: 1px solid #2a2a2a;
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 50px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .contact-box p {
            color: #aaa;
            font-size: 17px;
            margin-bottom: 28px;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }

        /* FOOTER */
        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 30px;
            color: #444;
            font-size: 13px;
            border-top: 1px solid #1a1a1a;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <!-- NAV -->
    <nav>
        <div class="logo">David Brilly</div>
        <ul>
            <li><a href="#about">About</a></li>
            <li><a href="#skills">Skills</a></li>
            <li><a href="#projects">Projects</a></li>
            <li><a href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
        </ul>
    </nav>

    <!-- HERO -->
    <div class="hero">
        <h1>Hi, I'm <span>David Brilly</span></h1>
        <p>A carpentry student with a passion for building things — whether it's with wood or code.</p>
        <a href="#contact" class="btn">Get in touch</a>
    </div>

    <!-- ABOUT -->
    <section id="about">
        <h2>About Me</h2>
        <p class="about-text">
            I'm David, a carpentry student from Slovenia. I love working with my hands and creating things that last. 
            Recently I've started exploring the world of web development — because building for the web is just another 
            form of craftsmanship. When I'm not in the workshop, you'll find me learning new skills and taking on new challenges.
        </p>
    </section>

    <!-- SKILLS -->
    <section id="skills">
        <h2>Skills</h2>
        <div class="skills-grid">
            <span class="skill-tag highlight">Carpentry</span>
            <span class="skill-tag highlight">Woodworking</span>
            <span class="skill-tag highlight">HTML</span>
            <span class="skill-tag highlight">CSS</span>
            <span class="skill-tag">Problem Solving</span>
            <span class="skill-tag">Attention to Detail</span>
            <span class="skill-tag">Teamwork</span>
            <span class="skill-tag">Fast Learner</span>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- PROJECTS -->
    <section id="projects">
        <h2>Projects</h2>
        <div class="projects-grid">
            <div class="project-card">
                <h3>My Portfolio</h3>
                <p>This website you're looking at right now. Built from scratch with HTML and CSS.</p>
                <span class="project-tag">HTML & CSS</span>
            </div>
            <div class="project-card">
                <h3>Coming Soon</h3>
                <p>My next project is already in the works. Stay tuned!</p>
                <span class="project-tag">In progress</span>
            </div>
            <div class="project-card">
                <h3>Coming Soon</h3>
                <p>More projects on the way as I keep learning and building.</p>
                <span class="project-tag">In progress</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CONTACT -->
    <section id="contact">
        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <div class="contact-box">
            <p>Have a question or want to work together? Feel free to reach out!</p>
            <a href="mailto:david.brilly09@gmail.com" class="btn">Send me an email</a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer>
        <p>© 2026 David Brilly — Built with ❤️ and a lot of curiosity</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
